quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  39,71,"Yeddu…ìe …ìen soggiroyee ka Jahannama dente-dente. Haa si …ìe hewtii nge, dame magge udditee, reenu…ìe nge …ìen wi'ana …ìe: \"E Nulaa…ìe jeyaa…ìe e mo'on hewtaano on, janngaynoo…ìe Aayeeje Joomi mon, e moo…óon, …ìe rentina on hawrugol e ndee √±alaande mon?\" ∆Åe wi'a: \"Ko non tigiri, kono Konngol lepte ngol, jojjiino e yeddu…ìe …ìen"
  39,72,"[∆Åe] wi'anee: \"Naatiree dame Jahannama …óen lutton ton. Nge bonii jaa∆¥orde mawnintinii…ìe …ìen"
  39,73,"Huloo…ìe Joomi mun …ìen kadi …óowitiree ka Aljanna, dente-dente. Haa si …ìe hewtii mo, dame makko udditee, reenu…ìe mo …ìen wi'ana …ìe: \"Kisiyee wonii e mon, on laa…ìii, naatiree mo, duumagol"
  39,74,"∆Åe wi'a ontuma: \"Yettoore woodanii Allah, laatinan…óo men fodoore Mun, O ronini men leydi [Aljanna] ndin, me…óen weerira e Aljanna on, kala ka men yi…ói\". Mbarjaari gollunoo…ìe mo∆¥∆¥ere …ìen mo∆¥∆¥ii"
  39,75,"Yi'oyaa Malaa'ikaen, hi…ìe taarii Arsi kin, hi…ìe subbunhinora yettugol Joomi ma…ì…ìe. Goonga √±aawiree hakkunde ma…ì…ìe. Wi'ee ontuma: \"Yettoore woodanii Allah, Jey…óo tegeefo ngon"